                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Knight</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Cape Town</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-02-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 7, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Preliminary examination now proceeding. Trial takes place 21st April. Hammond out
                    on bail—$50,000. He has been placed in cottage outside gaol under guard. Have
                    you received my cables dated 21st January? Reply.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Knight.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
